01:26:26.023 --> 01:26:29.777
Pazi kuda ideš drži se plana!

01:27:21.077 --> 01:27:23.079
Alice?

01:27:42.515 --> 01:27:46.268
Alice! Idi ravno naprijed!

01:27:56.487 --> 01:27:58.781
