01:30:36.894 --> 01:30:39.021
Jebi ga.

01:30:49.448 --> 01:30:52.493
U redu. Hajde, hajde,hajde!

01:30:55.621 --> 01:31:00.208
Alice dokle je došlo?
-75 %.

